                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-8">
                    <div class="sidebar-option">
                        <div class="so-latest">
                            <h5 class="title">Latest news</h5>
                            <div class="latest-large set-bg" data-setbg="./../../img/letest-blog/latest-1.jpeg">
                                <div class="ll-text">
                                    <h5><a href="#">Congratulations to the UTM-DOR team for the 1st place among the Superior Education Institutions</a></h5>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Nov 19, 2022</li>
                                        <li>20 Comment</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="latest-large set-bg" data-setbg="./../../img/letest-blog/latest-2.jpg">
                                <div class="ll-text">
                                    <h5><a href="#">Congratulations to Lilian Balan, student IMC-211, Faculty of Energy and Electrical Engineering, UTM</a></h5>
                                    <ul>
